node.text:
Here are some of my fav/go-to sets!!! Comment down below if you have any questions so I can answer those for you!!
-
I am an XS in EVERYTHING! For reference: 5ft tall | 105lbs | Waist: 23in
-
I will have a link in my bio + I will post swipe up links before the sale! If you choose to shop through my link it does support me directly 💛💖

Time to train BOULDER SHOULDERS 😮‍💨 focusing on that mind muscle connection with every rep! Let’s getttt it!

1️⃣ 3 sets / 8 (each) alternating lateral raise

2️⃣ 3 sets / 10 rear delt pull

3️⃣ 4 sets / 10 Arnold press

4️⃣ 3 sets / 8 (each) around the world into thumbs up lateral raise

5️⃣ 3 sets / 12 (each) single arm rear delt row

Wearing @gymshark x @whitneyysimmons coming soooooon!!
-
#bouldershoulders #shoulderworkout #fitness #fitmotivation #fit #motivation #shoulders #upperbodyworkout #workoutideas #gym #workoutvideo #workoutmotivation

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Alex Rice | Workouts on September 06, 2021. May be an image of 1 person, standing and shorts.

node.text:
Happy Monday 🍯🌻 What’re you training today?? Last week my workouts were a little all over the place, which is ok!! Buuut this week I’m getting them back in order! Not every workout will be some killer session, but we’re still showing up and putting the effort in 👏🏼 which is a win!!

Wearing @gymshark vital seamless 2.0 shorts + v neck training sports bra
-
#mondaymotivation #motivation #workout #legday #legworkout #mondayworkout #fit #fitmotivation #fitness #healthylifestyle #gymmotivation #fitnessmotivation #gym

Photo by Alex Rice | Workouts on September 06, 2021. May be an image of 1 person, standing and shorts.

node.text:
Killer LEG DAY 👏🏼 focused more on glutes and hamstrings for these 5 exercises!! Give this one a GOOO!

1️⃣ 3 sets / 10 DB sumo squats (slight pause at the bottom)

2️⃣ 3 sets / 10 (each) Bulgarian split squats

3️⃣ 4 sets / 10 sumo deadlifts

4️⃣ 3 sets / 12 (each) single leg glute bridge

5️⃣ 3 sets / 12 hamstring bridge- like a glute bridge but scoot away from the bench and let your hammies lift you up!

Wearing @gymshark flex cycle shorts + training bandeau // Song: Coupe by Pop Smoke
-
#legday #legsworkout #legworkout #fitness #fitmotivation #motivation #workout #gym #legdaymotivation #workoutmotivation #fit #liftweights #gettingfit

node.text:
Weekend workout coming right up 🤎 I usually have at least one weekend workout and the other day is more of a rest day and “get everything together for the upcoming week” day!
But first up for today is a run, then a leg day, then walkies 🐶🐶, and probably another pumpkin cream cold brew 😬 (anyone else!?)

Wearing @gymshark energy seamless shorts + v neck training sports bra
-

STRONG BACK + a little biceps and rear delts 😮‍💨 it’s a PULL day!! Don’t forget a solid warm up 👏🏼 Give this on a goooo!

1️⃣ 3 sets / 8-10 (each) static hold biceps curls

2️⃣ 3 sets / 8 single arm DB rows

3️⃣ 4 sets / 10 barbell bent over row

4️⃣ 3 sets / 12 incline rear delt rows

5️⃣ 2-3 sets / 6-8 (each) bear plank rows

Wearing @gymshark NEW adapt butterfly launching this Thursday! // Song: Coupe by Pop Smoke

Starting the week off with a GLUTE focused LEG DAY 👏🏼 what’re you training today?? Let’s gooooo!

1️⃣ 3 sets / 8 1 3/4 goblet squats

2️⃣ 3 sets / 10 (each) stationary lunges

3️⃣ 4 sets / 8 sumo deadlifts

4️⃣ 3 sets / 12 single leg DB hip thrusts

5️⃣ 3 sets / 10-12 DB RDLs

Wearing @gymshark vital seamless 2.0 // Song Rain On Me by Lady Gaga, Ariana Grande
-
#mondaylegday #legday #legworkout #legs #mondaymotivation #mondayworkout #gym #gymmotivation #motivation #workoutideas #workoutvideo #fitness

Wearing NEW Adapt Butterfly 🦋 @gymshark coming soooooooon!!

node.text:
Let’s train BOULDER SHOULDERS 👊🏼
the workout I look forward to the most each week 👏🏼 I was toast after this one!! Let’s GOOOO

1️⃣ 3 sets / 8-10 single arm lateral raise

2️⃣ 4 sets / 10 Arnold press

3️⃣ 3 sets / 12 chest supported rear delt fly

4️⃣ 3 sets / 10 rainbow front raises

5️⃣ 3 sets / 12 rear delt pulls

Wearing @gymshark Apex shorts + training bandeau // Song: Coupe by Pop Smoke
-
#bouldershoulders #workoutmotivation #motivation #shoulderworkout #shoulders #bouldershoulderworkout #dumbbellonly #homeworkout #upperbodyworkout #gettingfit
